        <Label layoutX="486.0" layoutY="168.0" prefHeight="84.0" prefWidth="480.0" text="1. Gently press the tofu between paper towels or a clean kitchen towel to remove excess moisture. Cut it into cubes." wrapText="true">
            <font>
                <Font size="15.0" />
            </font>
        </Label>
        <Label layoutX="486.0" layoutY="248.0" prefHeight="54.0" prefWidth="575.0" text="2. In a bowl, combine the 1 tablespoon of soy sauce and 1 tablespoon of cornstarch. Toss the tofu cubes in this mixture to coat them." wrapText="true">
