                <Font size="15.0" />
            </font>
        </Label>
        <Label layoutX="486.0" layoutY="303.0" prefHeight="99.0" prefWidth="538.0" text="3. Heat 2 tablespoons of vegetable oil in a large skillet or wok over medium-high heat. Add the tofu cubes and fry until they turn golden and crispy on all sides, about 5-7 minutes. Remove the tofu from the skillet and set it aside." wrapText="true">
