        <Label layoutX="483.0" layoutY="579.0" prefHeight="126.0" prefWidth="563.0" text="6. Add the diced red and green bell peppers to the skillet. Stir-fry for a few minutes until the peppers start to soften. Return the fried tofu to the skillet. Pour in the Kung Pao sauce. Stir everything together and allow the sauce to thicken, which should take about 2-3 minutes. Stir in the unsalted peanuts and sliced green onions. " wrapText="true">
